<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-3.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="image/topic_movies.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Movies</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How often do you go to the cinema?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you love movie ?.
I am a movie lover 
What is your favourite movie ?.
-> It is Harry Potter. -> Who is the director -> JK.rowling (director + author). -> It is famous or not ? -> It is one of the most famous film in the world -> What is type/genre (C1) of the movie ?. it is adventure kind of movie. -> It is gripping (lôi cuốn) and meaningful.
Do prefer to watch at home or go to the cinema ?.
i prefer to watch at home.
1. because it saves a lot of time and money -> i do not need to pay for ticket and move.
2. In modern world, all films have been on the Internet. It is free for everyone. So i can use Netflix to watch my favourite movies. 








</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-3.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
