                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What kind of movies do you like best ? Why ?.
-> I get interested in Fantasy kind of movie. 
Because my daily routine is repetitive so i want to explore new experiences. and Fantasy movie helps me to be creative, have purposes (mục đích) in life. 
like = facinated by = get interested in = keen on  
